               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) ዳዊት, Psalter I-<locus target="#1"/>) መዝሙረ፡ዳዊት“Psalms of  David” (fols. <locus from="3r" to="115v"/>) I-<locus target="#2"/>) መኃልየ፡ነቢያት፡ወጸሎቱ፡ ለሙሴ“The Canticles of the Prophets and the Prayer of Moses” (fols. <locus from="116r" to="127v"/>) I-<locus target="#3"/>) መኃልየ፡መኃልይ፡ዘውእቱ፡ ሰሎሞን“Song of Songs of Solomon” (fols. <locus from="127v" to="132v"/>) I-<locus target="#4"/>) ውዳሴ፡ማርያም“The Praise of Mary” (fols. <locus from="133ra" to="141rb"/>) </p>
                     <p>I-<locus target="#5"/>) አንቀጸ፡ብርሃን“Gate of Light” (fols. <locus from="141rb" to="144vb"/>)</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
              
